{"tid":1205452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗蠢到用返工個電話開telegram","createTime":"2019-06-11T18:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T15:17:02.000Z","uid":147036,"like":910,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"b17013ceaeb232c32cf81541147ca6c416c62406","tid":1205452,"uid":147036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"第一次喺連登開post 仲要係借人ac<br />\n估唔到就係講呢啲話題<br />\n<br />\n我上年年尾有啲私事要去警署處理<br />\n咁嗰陣有個黑警聯絡我 <br />\n所以我就有呢隻狗嘅contact<br />\n頭先開tg想睇現場最新消息 <br />\n點知俾我見到下面呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPHVDKr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPHVDKr.png&h=9ff62319&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QS1n3bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQS1n3bb.png&h=c8d63d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位黎警長係灣仔區警民關係科/學校聯絡小組嘅人員<br />\n隻狗好可能已經subscribe咗同今次有關嘅各大channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大家都一早知啲狗會四圍套料<br />\n但照計都係開太空卡/唔用電話號碼開telegram戶口吖<br />\n會唔會係蠢到用自己平時開工做嘢嗰個no嚟開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要明顯到喺呢啲時勢咁樣開法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都諗咗幾耐 睇哂全個熱門都冇點見有人講呢樣 所以先決定開呢個post<br />\n講嚟都未必有用 但都係想行動緊嘅大家小心<br />\n<br />\n上面show咗隻狗嘅電話號碼<br />\n不過我唔鼓勵大家打去問候佢屋企人/幫佢嗌外賣<br />\n陣間人地話你阻差辦公 不斷打電話罪就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(利申：絕非借刀)"},{"pid":"033cd10b48ea11f5d2a0cc93a235c3178aa8e155","tid":1205452,"uid":100331,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:00:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc592e56c6325670bf5dcab9997a43419e21bdb6","tid":1205452,"uid":88582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5e1076d4c8be5e9ac0aff53c45239e283602a6","tid":1205452,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd9f37b12fd4a6fdb672b96d8c78baf5965e9b2","tid":1205452,"uid":64560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a26a3ddbc330dc943cc07a06c3ed82ee7986d88","tid":1205452,"uid":34945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7c96c44de5b57947bbdb5a02cfa712282e9117","tid":1205452,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c579b3e8b46c6ad865e7dce937272e3c4bb4f87d","tid":1205452,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:04:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1facd01742117f93507b9ae9c1bd868d68af4eb","tid":1205452,"uid":85980,"like":137,"dislike":5,"score":132,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:04:57.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借借位!<br />\n宗教理念未必一致, 但目標係一樣!!! <br />\n上街，卻似無法撼動政府的立場，我們還能作甚麼呢？在這個漸趨黑暗的日子，求你賜你的子民勇氣、信心及忍耐，堅守拒絕謊言、與受壓逼者同行、在絕望中活出美善以照亮別人的底線。<br />\n<br />\n願弟兄姊妹不分你我一同禱告，願上主憐憫。<br />\n<br />\n香港基督教教牧聯署籌委會 <br />\n早禱會<br />\n<br />\n日期: 2019.6.12<br />\n時間: 7:30-8:30<br />\n地點: 政府總部外<br />\n講員: 邢福增院長 <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fbne3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62512634_2342108942501590_5474578908500197376_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEEa8YKWC2Gbx6sFNSWJsGbZqiS8-kUk1bxTcvnK_UysHrZhr-x4fU8Ij_0QaaJBLCdYfLUYM_w3BjyUukX-Qfi5L_voDS80mhrazWKb5MGFA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fbne3-1.fna&amp;oh=2c2c