src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPHVDKr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPHVDKr.png&h=9ff62319&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QS1n3bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQS1n3bb.png&h=c8d63d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位黎警長係灣仔區警民關係科/學校聯絡小組嘅人員<br />\n隻狗好可能已經subscribe咗同今次有關嘅各大channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大家都一早知啲狗會四圍套料<br />\n但照計都係開太空卡/唔用電話號碼開telegram戶口吖<br />\n會唔會係蠢到用自己平時開工做嘢嗰個no嚟開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要明顯到喺呢啲時勢咁樣開法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都諗咗幾耐 睇哂全個熱門都冇點見有人講呢樣 所以先決定開呢個post<br />\n講嚟都未必有用 但都係想行動緊嘅大家小心<br />\n<br />\n上面show咗隻狗嘅電話號碼<br />\n不過我唔鼓勵大家打去問候佢屋企人/幫佢嗌外賣<br />\n陣間人地話你阻差辦公 不斷打電話罪就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(利申：絕非借刀)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:47:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57d78f2cf70aa013a91b56b6809e8e4a3c485b19","tid":1205452,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:55:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6202754be050f90c9ef5b2f9567e3975dec390c","tid":1205452,"uid":51965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:56:14.000Z","msg":"我個中同都開左tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc1a3ccb707b8b74b39fa3697a039f319ae5f7c","tid":1205452,"uid":185215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:59:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d1a2af6c4d6c63ea1b4b06e27d8b42ddd4bb7ad","tid":1205452,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc71b525cbe61e2ce37980077cad1685975cbb81"